snippet.title: Dunk Dunk | Release Date Announcement!
snippet.description:
Dunk Dunk is SHOOTIN' its way onto PC and Switch on May 8th! 

PC: https://bit.ly/4jUtFrG
Switch: https://bit.ly/4hTOCAU

There's chaotic party gaming, basketballing action for all in Dunk Dunk! Play through the singleplayer Galaxy Tour or take on your friends in a sofa showdown with up to 4 players!
